presencia multiregional. Actualmente cuenta con más de 60 planteles a lo largo de la República Mexicana.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHoy INTERLINGUA® está presente en el Distrito Federal y en 22 estados del país.','Acerca de Interlingua','','publish','open','open','','acerca-de-interlingua','','','2013-09-06 17:25:27','2013-09-06 17:25:27','',0,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?page_id=522',0,'page','',0),(376,1,'2013-08-29 20:42:49','2013-08-29 20:42:49','','Interlingua Satélite','','inherit','open','open','','375-revision-v1','','','2013-08-29 20:42:49','2013-08-29 20:42:49','',375,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?p=376',0,'revision','',0),(377,1,'2013-08-29 21:32:29','2013-08-29 21:32:29','Ingresa en esta sección la información de el plantel','Plantel','','publish','open','open','','plantel','','','2013-09-02 15:54:00','2013-09-02 15:54:00','',0,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?wp-types-group=plantel',0,'wp-types-group','',0),(379,1,'2013-08-29 21:57:10','2013-08-29 21:57:10','','Interlingua Satélite','','inherit','open','open','','375-revision-v1','','','2013-08-29 21:57:10','2013-08-29 21:57:10','',375,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?p=379',0,'revision','',0),(380,1,'2013-08-29 22:32:40','2013-08-29 22:32:40','','Descubre nuestros planteles','','publish','open','open','','descubre-nuestros-planteles-2','','','2013-09-10 22:35:41','2013-09-10 22:35:41','',0,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?p=380',33,'nav_menu_item','',0),(378,1,'2013-08-29 21:34:12','2013-08-29 21:34:12','[mcf id=\"map_canvas\" width=\"100%\" height=\"550px\" map_center=\"19.497755,-99.237796\" map_zoom=\"13\" listener=\"mouseover\" locations=\"(Interlingua_Satélite, 19.497755, -99.237796, office_red, daniel@clicker360.com), industry_blue, factory@domain.xx)\"]','Interlingua Satélite','','inherit','open','open','','375-revision-v1','','','2013-08-29 21:34:12','2013-08-29 21:34:12','',375,'http://dev.clicker360.com/interlingua_sitio/?p=378',0,